    "description": "This effortless showstopper is packed with aromatic flavour. You'll simmer meat-free chick'n in a rich, ras el hanout-spiced tomato sauce before stirring through lentils. Serve your tagine with garlicky couscous on the side and tuck in. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
