    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meat-free chick'n </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to brown</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/meat-free-chick-n-and-lentil-tagine-with-herby-couscous/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Top, tail and dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Rinse your <strong>red lentils</strong> in a sieve under <strong>cold running water</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/meat-free-chick-n-and-lentil-tagine-with-herby-couscous/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>diced carrot </strong>and <strong>most </strong>of the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(save the rest for later!) to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/meat-free-chick-n-and-lentil-tagine-with-herby-couscous/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[600ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/meat-free-chick-n-and-lentil-tagine-with-herby-couscous/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Re-boil half a kettle</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>rinsed lentils </strong>and <strong>ras el hanout </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 30 secs, stirring to coat the grains</p><p>Add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>and <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar </strong>and cook, covered, for 14-16 min or until the lentils are almost cooked</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/meat-free-chick-n-and-lentil-tagine-with-herby-couscous/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>couscous</strong> to a heatproof bowl with 130ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[190ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[260ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and the <strong>remaining garlic</strong>, cover with <strong>cling film</strong> and set aside until all of the liquid has been absorbed</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the couscous<strong> </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>pepper</strong> and fluff with a fork<strong> </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>herby couscous</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/meat-free-chick-n-and-lentil-tagine-with-herby-couscous/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the lentils are tender, remove the lid and cook for a further 1-2 min or until the sauce has thickened \u2013 this is your <strong>meat-free chick'n & lentil tagine</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/meat-free-chick-n-and-lentil-tagine-with-herby-couscous/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>meat-free chick'n & lentil tagine </strong>to the side of the <strong>herby couscous</strong></p><p>Sprinkle with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and your <strong>black sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
